1778650121912448	maw-dev	itc:v3:AWKTmSTM_JOSSTQAAAAAQa7Vbfq6qsAAAAEyzA0		item.comment	bn-5kad	{"body":"bn-175a triage complete. Per-file production count delta in scope:\n\n- epoch_gc.rs: 0 (confirmed: all 12 matches are #[cfg(test)] fixtures, no production work needed)\n- ref_gc.rs: 1 -> 0 (committer_time added to CommitInfo)\n- doctor.rs: 4 -> 1 (check_git_head/is_inside_worktree/is_registered_worktree migrated; remaining call is get_git_version which is an intentional diagnostic probe of the user installed git binary)\n- upgrade.rs: 4 -> 2 (clean_root_source_files via walk_tree_blob_paths; warn_remaining_untracked_root_files via list_untracked; remaining 2 are fix_git_head symbolic-ref ops, TODO(gix): no symbolic_ref primitive on GitRepo trait yet)\n- maw-tui/app.rs: 6 -> 6 (TODO(gix) carveouts; maw-tui has no maw-git dep, RepoDataSource trait would need to grow ref/diff/log primitives; tracked here)\n- maw-assurance oracle.rs: 7 -> 7 (assurance carveouts: oracle is intentionally an *independent* verifier; using git CLI keeps it distinct from the gix code paths it is verifying, so a bug in gix cannot mask an invariant violation. Recommend keeping these permanent.)\n- maw-assurance trace.rs: 3 -> 3 (same assurance rationale)\n- workspace/{mod,undo,history}.rs: 3 -> 3 (already had TODO(gix); needs --git-common-dir / worktree-undo / log-format primitives)\n\nNet: 27 -> 21 production calls in bn-175a scope (-6).\n\nNew primitive: CommitInfo.committer_time: i64 (mirrors git log -1 --format=%ct). Used by ref_gc.\n\nSuggested follow-ups (out of bn-175a scope):\n1. Extend RepoDataSource (maw-tui) with epoch_hash, epoch_diff, commit_info, dirty_files: unlocks 6 tui carveouts.\n2. Add GitRepo::symbolic_ref(name, target) and GitRepo::read_symbolic_ref(name): unlocks 2 upgrade.rs + 1 doctor.rs (clean reimpl).\n3. Consider whether maw-assurance carveouts should be made permanent (like push/fetch) given the independence rationale. They are the strongest defense against a gix-induced silent invariant break."}	blake3:9LGwpepWZes6wdHHcLe0p-iPQxjojXkX7qy1ygjsHoc
