1778861449585318	maw-dev	itc:v3:AWKTmSTM_JOSSTQAAAAAQa7Vbfq6qsAAAAEy1A0		item.create	bn-pfh7	{"description":"Fresh-eyes review of gix migration since v0.60.9. status() is index->worktree only; worktree_state_commit, diff_name_status_pairs (snapshot), and recover dest_has_uncommitted all need HEAD->worktree. Staged-only changes silently dropped -> quarantine promotes unfixed tree, merge snapshot loses staged work, --restore-file clobbers staged work. Also: stat_matches_by_content symlink to_string_lossy miscount; find_entry_at_path rejects ./ components contradicting validate_show_path.","kind":"bug","title":"fix(gix): status_head_to_worktree drops staged-only changes (Prime Invariant)"}	blake3:KfLU63Ap8smvc_iF8vvfFzmJot7XrXsd1LLDIoHExRw
