1778959649819074	maw-dev	itc:v3:AWKTmSTM_JOSSTQAAAAAQa7Vbfq6qsAAAAEy_g0		item.comment	bn-cm63	{"body":"Root cause confirmed + fixed in ws/bn-cm63 (commit d56cbf6). destroy now refuses during a Live in-flight merge (Orphaned/Indeterminate -> merge --abort hint, preserves bn-2wyh); plain 'maw gc' self-heals dangling refs/manifold/head/* (skips live-merge sources). Regression tests added. just check green (3025 tests); chaos repro 0 leaks / 5 runs (pre-fix 3/3 leaked). NOT merged -- awaiting lead review."}	blake3:SaksM0R28qOEuXBxJTOUL32LLjvpAZJCjO-CDezG3WM
