1778964381960585	maw-dev	itc:v3:AWKTmSTM_JOSSTQAAAAAQa7Vbfq6qsAAAAEynQ4		item.create	bn-1c2m	{"description":"Root = normal checkout doubling as merge target; agent worktrees under\n.maw/worktrees/. Specify discovery, workspace_path resolution, .gitignore\nsemantics, how the engine updates the privileged root checkout (reuse\nsync_target_worktree_to_epoch / FF-absorb), and the v2 ws/ -> new-layout\nmigration. Done when: design reviewed and the engine-impact is shown to be\nrelocation, not rewrite.\n","kind":"task","labels":["v1-0","layout"],"parent":"bn-2yh1","size":"m","title":"T3.1 Layout design doc + migration/back-compat plan"}	blake3:c8k2IjgZciIa4VztHIjlt-Aip9Ew_uI13cH1sxeTroY
