1779056917110308	maw-dev	itc:v3:AWKTmSTM_JOSSTQAAAAAQa7Vbfq6qsAAAAEy9Q8		item.comment	bn-2ixm	{"body":"SP3 done. jj opfork-wedge REPRODUCED on jj 0.41.0 (concurrent 3-ws burst): 'sibling of the working copy operation' Internal error x7, 4 divergent change-ids, 11 reconcile-divergent ops, agent forced to abandon work to recover. §2.2 #3/#4/#5 all observed -> jj arm is FAIR, not strawman. Harness: claude -p --output-format json (feasible; --bare breaks OAuth, use /tmp isolation). Cost $0.077/agent happy (CV 4.8%, turns CV 9.5%), $0.137 wedged (~1.8x). N~7-10/arm; size on wedge-incidence (bimodal). Deliverable: ws/bn-2ixm/notes/agent-benchmark-feasibility.md. Committed 342b974, NOT merged."}	blake3:RE41JQZQOKcQB4yeMCOUOSsOQllU6624LyMF8hXZWxs
