1779061819560478	maw-dev	itc:v3:AWKTmSTM_JOSSTQAAAAAQa7Vbfq6qsAAAAEyhxA		item.comment	bn-kwm7	{"body":"Done (pending lead review/merge). notes/sg1-dst-architecture.md committed in ws/bn-kwm7 (2d5323c4). Adopts SP1 HYBRID model + MAW_FP env bridge + pinned-git-date determinism contract; SP2 Oracle A=blob-reachability W subset U(F) (NOT ancestry), Oracle B=B1-B4 w/ staleness guard, incremental design mandated. Generator = driver-agnostic ScenarioPlan stream consumed identically by SG1 in-proc driver AND SG2/T2.1 real-agent driver (build once, drive two ways). Enumerated 8 remaining SG1 tasks; critical path T1.1->T1.2->{T1.3||T1.4||T1.5}->T1.6->T1.7->T1.8->T1.9. Flags: bn-1cww must land on main + bn-263u depends on it; T1.3 heavier than bone implies (must replace proven-wrong check_g1_reachability)."}	blake3:3Z0-PFuizsvnFA2NtfFX9T1pYxA_HPBmoMjNfe82kzE
