1778453173953215	maw-dev	itc:v3:AWKTmSTM_JOSSTQAAAAAQa7Vbfq6qsAAAAEyuw0		item.create	bn-ske8	{"description":"Roll up bn-3r8s, bn-2upt, bn-28q2, bn-sgm8, bn-103k, bn-3mbj, bn-3vf5, bn-11ip, bn-3az5, bn-17km, bn-qw4i, bn-3fhj, bn-6q05 into v0.60.8.","kind":"task","size":"s","title":"release v0.60.8"}	blake3:8cQevZ8GXiuWiinbtMrMATuUL-7icJhwgCyBN8x9-ts
