1778863659502876	maw-dev	itc:v3:AWKTmSTM_JOSSTQAAAAAQa7Vbfq6qsAAAAEy1g0		item.create	bn-uyk3	{"description":"Second fresh-eyes pass over the gix migration since v0.60.9 found 6 verified correctness bugs: (1) list_untracked collapses untracked dirs -> recovery snapshot data loss; (2) workspace_has_uncommitted_changes sync gate misses staged-only (bn-pfh7 class); (3) snapshot_working_copy misses staged-only; (4) FF-absorb drops exec bit / corrupts symlinks; (5) diff_name_status_pairs resurrects added-then-worktree-deleted file; (6) bf_get_dirty_files under-reports staged + wrong comment.","kind":"task","title":"fix(gix): fresh-eyes correctness bugs in gix migration (post v0.60.9)"}	blake3:SaRZezSEF_l1x3hVza_N_F8Hu7yzqTm1VUqh650dZSM
