1778964385039384	maw-dev	itc:v3:AWKTmSTM_JOSSTQAAAAAQa7Vbfq6qsAAAAEyqw4		item.create	bn-3qg7	{"description":"Architecture doc: scenario generator + fault injection + Oracle A + Oracle\nB + shrinker. Inventory and map maw-assurance (oracle/model/trace), the\nFP_* failpoints, recovery refs, and the merge-state FSM to the missing\ntop-level loop. Formally state both oracles as checkable predicates.\nDone when: doc reviewed; the ~30% missing surface is enumerated as the\nother SG1 tasks.\n","kind":"task","labels":["v1-0","dst"],"parent":"bn-3nw1","size":"m","title":"T1.1 Design DST architecture + inventory existing primitives"}	blake3:u4Mj-ENrISSZ-0BFaT58AXDEx5XFSMYauCDo61ev8yU
1778964385287545	maw-dev	itc:v3:AWKTmSTM_JOSSTQAAAAAQa7Vbfq6qsAAAAEyrA4		item.create	bn-1ztm	{"description":"Generate random VALID op-sequences over N workspaces (create/edit/commit/\nmerge/sync/destroy/recover). Parameterized condition spectrum: concurrency\ndegree, mid-op kill probability, overlapping-edit rate, stale-workspace\nrate. Fully deterministic from a seed. This is the SHARED substrate also\nconsumed by SG2's agent benchmark — design the interface accordingly.\nDone when: a seed reproduces an identical op-sequence + condition profile.\n","kind":"task","labels":["v1-0","dst"],"parent":"bn-3nw1","size":"l","title":"T1.2 Scenario + condition generator (shared substrate)"}	blake3:ebRn3hrd0ewu69gchvwm_fklof1V-uannb4VRh1B8MI
1778964385536462	maw-dev	itc:v3:AWKTmSTM_JOSSTQAAAAAQa7Vbfq6qsAAAAEyrQ4		item.create	bn-2m64	{"description":"After every step, assert: every commit ever reachable from any workspace\nref is still reachable from (default history) UNION (recovery refs) UNION\n(extant workspace refs). Track the historical set across the run. Done\nwhen: deliberately injecting a work-loss bug is caught with a minimal\nseed.\n","kind":"task","labels":["v1-0","dst"],"parent":"bn-3nw1","size":"l","title":"T1.3 Oracle A — no committed work lost (reachability)"}	blake3:3WdBpGvsW7qQZzZp8n85P1ITkXT5gkAQ30yMCc_wIWI
1778964385782480	maw-dev	itc:v3:AWKTmSTM_JOSSTQAAAAAQa7Vbfq6qsAAAAEyrg4		item.create	bn-2a5l	{"description":"After every step, assert: no dangling refs/manifold/head/* for\nnon-existent workspaces; merge-state.json consistent with refs; no\norphaned recovery. Must catch bn-cm63-class coherence bugs (bn-cm63 lost\nno work but was a real coherence defect doctor caught). Done when: a\nsynthetic bn-cm63 reproduction is flagged by the oracle.\n","kind":"task","labels":["v1-0","dst"],"parent":"bn-3nw1","size":"m","title":"T1.4 Oracle B — state coherence"}	blake3:NvtK-Z2G-o16ACy-oGgC65EWHyFMBEBZLkuXQspISLQ
