1779742500750998	maw-dev	itc:v3:AWKTmSTM_JOSSTQAAAAAQa7Vbfq6qsAAAAEy8xA		item.comment	bn-221b	{"body":"Implemented stale-state-self-healing legs (1) `maw status --json` enriched with `current_workspace[_state]`, per-ws `lifecycle_state`+`fix_command`, `stale_workspaces[]`, `integrate_ready[]` — all in one call; (2) `LifecycleState` safe-cleanup vocab (clean/dirty-uncommitted/committed-unintegrated/stale/conflicted/missing/integrated, kebab-case JSON). Stale ws excluded from `integrate_ready` to block doomed-merge wasted turns. Event-log leg deferred (NOTE for SG4 triage: helps `ws_recover_invoked`/`read_from_stale_workspace` clusters more — their own children). Layout-agnostic via `WorkspaceInfo.path`. Tests: 12 unit + 7 integration; full suite 3084 pass / 0 fail; clippy clean."}	blake3:G9xVo0ctdgIiNzcLk8ENnUW1UiNInKXDQuL5b3QTfZ0
