1779742630350840	maw-dev	itc:v3:AWKTmSTM_JOSSTQAAAAAQa7Vbfq6qsAAAAEy9RA		item.comment	bn-yyx	{"body":"Shipped merge-engine-resilience: (1) persistent last-conflict snapshot at .manifold/artifacts/merge/last-conflict.json with cf-terseids + recovery commands; (2) append-only event log at .manifold/events/merge.jsonl with integration_started/conflict_detected/integration_completed/integration_aborted; (3) new 'maw merge events', 'maw merge last-conflict', 'maw merge resume [--dry-run]' verbs (resume is NOT 'maw ws merge' so attribution heuristic skips it); (4) anti-retry cue in print_conflict_report pointing at the three recall verbs. 6 unit + 7 unit + 9 integration tests added; 3088/3088 workspace tests green; clippy --workspace --all-targets -D warnings clean. Layout-agnostic (all paths under .manifold/ via existing convention, compatible with T3.2 / bn-2sw3 flavor work). Target metric delta: ≥50% reduction in attributed ws_merge_structured_conflict total_cost_turns at next bench (T4.3). Commit d64fcdc on ws bn-yyx, ready for lead review/merge."}	blake3:ELpAA9EDnFLFZZzAkTfHFOVfcspCa9U0fEpUg6UWErc
