1779743810314961	maw-dev	itc:v3:AWKTmSTM_JOSSTQAAAAAQa7Vbfq6qsAAAAEy9xA		item.comment	bn-1ieb	{"body":"Implemented epoch-auto-advance mitigation across 3 surfaces sharing one classifier (crates/maw-cli/src/workspace/epoch_drift.rs): (1) architectural auto_advance_if_safe reuses ff_absorb safety predicate; (2) maw doctor gains check_epoch_drift + new --repair flag that runs the safe advance; (3) maw status --json gains epoch_drift field (4-state: in_sync/ff_absorbable/ff_blocked/diverged) so machine consumers see drift without a second tool call. 13 new tests (7 unit + 6 integration + 3 doctor + 4 status) all green; 3062 workspace tests pass; clippy -D warnings clean. No other cluster degraded — no semantic changes to existing verbs, --repair gated, layout-agnostic. Commit f7b985c8."}	blake3:K7qMNNL-CRW8_Y9Zt3PHCOM7t7Ur8b0KA7v-v6ssTaY
