1779751863307358	maw-dev	itc:v3:AWKTmSTM_JOSSTQAAAAAQa7Vbfq6qsAAAAEynBE		item.comment	bn-1uzn	{"body":"T3.5 harness shipped: sg3-layout-eval binary + decide_go_no_go (R1-R6 verbatim from bn-iux4 §3.1) + planted-regression pilot tests + notes/sg3-go-no-go.md scaffold. Pilot GREEN (GO on identical substrates, NO-GO on planted R1, < 60s wall). just sg3-prereg-check + just sg3-layout-eval-pilot both green. Real-LLM campaign (~$5-8, ~30-60 min wall, frozen N=20/10) gated on T3.2/T3.3 + bootstrap pipeline; verdict slot in notes/sg3-go-no-go.md §0 is empty until run. SG5 reads the doc; NO-GO is acceptable per bn-iux4 §5 (v1.0 ships on ws/, SG3 → v1.1)."}	blake3:Y80SqQmVREFgxkFEk0ZO6xqoYPyh5qBVg_VHA7Fo7sI
