1779891367666702	maw-dev	itc:v3:AWKTmSTM_JOSSTQAAAAAQa7Vbfq6qsAAAAEyzxE		item.comment	bn-f5zu	{"body":"Implemented. ws/bn-f5zu commit 58e1198. New modules: maw_bench::version_capture (capture_versions -> ToolVersion {maw,git,jj}) and maw_bench_sweep::preflight (check_maw_version_skew, WARN-only). harness::build_manifest now populates maw_version (was empty); git/jj/maw versions all per-run, ms-fast. sg3-layout-eval + sg2-sweep-pilot bins call preflight at main entry. 14 new tests pass (5 version_capture + 2 harness manifest + 7 preflight). cargo check --workspace, cargo clippy --workspace --all-targets -D warnings, cargo test --workspace all green. notes/sg2-benchmark-preregistration.md §6.4 documents the populated-fields contract."}	blake3:hzRk_6URQjSIePip7s1nx49u-OTA2IXgF5r_E84LE_w
