1779909223904987	maw-dev	itc:v3:AWKTmSTM_JOSSTQAAAAAQa7Vbfq6qsAAAAEy2BE		item.comment	bn-1pzb	{"body":"Root cause: H8 (metric artifact). Substring heuristic counts task-required 'maw ws recover' as friction; is_maw_arm misses 'maw@<flavor>' arms; median×n proxy amplifies 1-vs-0 lower-median to 10×; unpaired per-arm seeds randomly gave new 5 RC tasks vs old 4. Raw sums 7 (new) vs 6 (old) = noise. Layout fine. Fix: 3-line patch to extract.rs::is_maw_arm + attribution.rs (task-aware recover) + sg3_decision.rs::sum_proxy (raw sum). NO re-run needed. See notes/sg3-no-go-rootcause-v2.md §§3,5."}	blake3:if16yrOCPuUpckyI1A75YuQwmhSTxWhzpehvg6AhUOo
1779909230667355	maw-dev	itc:v3:AWKTmSTM_JOSSTQAAAAAQa7Vbfq6qsAAAAEy2RE		item.comment	bn-3uj4	{"body":"v1.0-pre.1 layout recommendation (revised from bn-2ert/bn-1pzb): ship .maw/ consolidated default; SG3 R6 NO-GO is a bench-metric artifact (H8), NOT a layout regression. 3-line metric fix needed (extract.rs::is_maw_arm to match 'maw@<flavor>' + attribution.rs task-aware recover + sg3_decision.rs raw-sum proxy). No fresh eval-run required: existing rerun data yields R6 PASS_EQUIVALENT once fixed (raw 7-vs-6 sum). See notes/sg3-no-go-rootcause-v2.md §6."}	blake3:j-mfXEZbORuhvpF9docjLlbrbS70JHr4SY2gGYtFkI8
