1779911970713987	maw-dev	itc:v3:AWKTmSTM_JOSSTQAAAAAQa7Vbfq6qsAAAAEy3xE		item.comment	bn-27ai	{"body":"3 fixes landed (commit 27ef92f7): A.1 is_maw_arm + maw@<flavor>; A.2 (α) count_recover_tasks_in_prompt subtracts task-required recovers from WsRecoverInvoked; A.3 CellAggregate.sum + sum_proxy raw-sum (median×n fallback for legacy summaries). Tests: 13 in metrics + 4 in sweep. Offline recompute (new bin sg3-recompute-decision) yields raw 12v8 at C2-T0 (not 10v0) and 37v34 at C0-T0 — both R6 Fail honest deltas. Verdict still NO-GO but artifact 10× amplification gone; bn-1pzb's '7v6 → PASS' assumed the substring heuristic continued to apply, whereas A.1 routes through T2.5 which counts every invocation. Agents fumble recover flags ~3x per task (vocabulary scarcity, not layout shape). Lead decides bn-3uj4 between (a) ship + document, (b) defer + address scarcity, (c) defer + Fix B paired seeds."}	blake3:INWASs9X64KC8svayKGJrM4aFOicmbp_aeoBdSrIYJk
1779911986378925	maw-dev	itc:v3:AWKTmSTM_JOSSTQAAAAAQa7Vbfq6qsAAAAEy4BE		item.comment	bn-3uj4	{"body":"bn-27ai landed (commit 27ef92f7). SG3 metric pipeline is now honest: raw per-replicate sums replace median×n. Recomputed verdict (notes/eval-real-2026-05-27/sg3-rerun-recomputed/) is STILL NO-GO at R6 — but the 10v0 amplification artifact is gone; honest deltas are 37v34 at C0 and 12v8 at C2. The friction is vocabulary-scarcity-shaped (agents fumble recover --to vs --into ~3x per task), not layout-shape-shaped (bn-1pzb §2 H7 still refuted). Three options: (a) ship .maw/ default for pre.1 and document the small R6 delta in the release notes (recommended — pre.1 is for dogfooding, the delta is sub-1-event per replicate); (b) defer the default-switch and address recover vocabulary first (orthogonal to layout); (c) defer + Fix B paired seeds (variance reduction). Lead decides."}	blake3:9qk93QcSwfhCaMSwOUlj27vj4h3_vHhh6fYGpwtC5Ms
