1779914443964639	maw-dev	itc:v3:AWKTmSTM_JOSSTQAAAAAQa7Vbfq6qsAAAAEy7BE		item.comment	bn-3w0c	{"body":"Implemented in ws/bn-3w0c (commit 9a1ab285):\n- SweepDriver::with_agent_config(Option<AgentConfig>) — None preserves AgentConfig::default() sonnet pin (SP3 §8.6).\n- sg2-sweep-pilot + sg3-layout-eval: --model=<id> CLI flag; default unchanged.\n- Justfile: sg2-sweep-real / sg3-layout-eval-real gain positional model='' arg (empty omits flag).\n- notes/sg2-benchmark-preregistration.md §8.6: cross-model-spot-check addendum (per-campaign discipline preserved).\n- Driver test asserts override flows into manifest.claude_model_id; default → 'sonnet'. cargo check + tests (0 failures) + targeted clippy: all green. Ready for lead review/merge."}	blake3:vyt5xVM9SMlKC1UrsCjqQi1IjqymKjs1V0Mw9qZl0bU
